---
import { siteMeta } from '../data/site';
---

<section class="hero-scene chapter-section" id="hero" data-video-scene="hero">
  <div class="hero-ritual">
    <p class="eyebrow hero-status">Operator / Live from Costa Rica</p>
    <h1 data-split>Fun, useful systems from a designer/operator in the jungle.</h1>
    <p class="hero-lede">
      I build across AI, automation, growth, venture systems, and public founder storytelling. The work lives between polished agency craft, practical product architecture, and the slightly weird momentum that makes the internet feel alive.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-signal-strip" aria-label="Current operating profile">
      <span><strong>01</strong> KR8TiV AI / software + agents</span>
      <span><strong>02</strong> KR8TiV Agency / positioning + growth</span>
      <span><strong>03</strong> Public builder logs / Costa Rica signal</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="action-primary" href={siteMeta.bookingUrl}>Book a meeting</a>
      <a class="action-secondary" href="/links/">Open the library</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <aside class="hero-aside" aria-label="Current signal">
    <span class="card-eyebrow">Current frequency</span>
    <h3>Bright, useful, a little feral, and still built to ship.</h3>
    <p>I like beautiful surfaces that have teeth: launch systems, AI workflows, GTM structure, product taste, and public work that compounds instead of disappearing into a private-notes swamp.</p>
  </aside>
</section>
